title: Điểm dừng chân Chợ Nổi Cái Răng
address: Đ. Võ Tánh, Lê Bình, Cái Răng, Cần Thơ

reviews.name: Văn Thi Thái
reviews.review: But when I returned to the floating market to visit the tour at dawn, all the other worries seemed to be relieved, and my soul felt like it was taken back to the origin where my parents used to trade on the floating market river, those are beautiful memories that I can never forget! Thank you for still preserving the culture!

reviews.name: Hải Trương Ngọc (Hari Truong)
reviews.review: A place worth experiencing about river tourism, we find the authenticity of Westerners. They are so refreshing and generous.

reviews.name: trang le
reviews.review: Going to the floating market during floating season is not much, because the fruit season is over. This place is probably only sold to tourists now, the price is quite expensive compared to outside. But also an interesting experience

reviews.name: Tien Nguyen
reviews.review: There are too many storks cursing at each other
